policies.name: Managers can view transactions for their units
policies.qual:
(EXISTS ( SELECT 1
   FROM (eshop.unit_bank_accounts uba
     JOIN unit_users uu ON ((uba.unit = uu.unit)))
  WHERE ((uba.bank_account = transactions.bank_account_id) AND (uu."user" = auth.uid()) AND (uu.is_manager = true))))
